> job control (disown is not a sufficient method in a function) is to
> unsetopt MONITOR, spawn the job, then setopt MONITOR again.  This
> nearly works.  Unfortunately,
> 
> % unsetopt monitor
> % sleep 30 &
> % setopt monitor
> % jobs
